{"tid":741488,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"仙人故 -《死亡》","createTime":"2018-07-13T16:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T10:46:30.000Z","uid":23479,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6e60f8d12dd8e1f0f97303339eba9cc259f5a6","tid":741488,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"每個人都害怕死亡，而每個人都不知道自己何時會<br />\n<br />\n死，更不會知道如何死去，但...如果有日，你可以<br />\n<br />\n看到別人的死亡時間......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年6月30日下午三時二十分，這就是站在我前<br />\n<br />\n面正在等待巴士的男人，他的死亡時間！<br />\n<br />\n我擁有比陰陽眼更麻煩的能力，沒錯！死亡之眼，<br />\n<br />\n我每日看到的除了一起和我上班的人，更看到他們<br />\n<br />\n頭上倒數著的時間！<br />\n<br />\n「老婆！你今晚記得拎蛋糕呀！阿仔生日我會盡量趕返嚟！」<br />\n<br />\n我在旁邊聽到這句話，但可惜......一小時二十分後，<br />\n<br />\n你將會迎接死亡，你不會再有機會回家和你兒子慶<br />\n<br />\n祝。<br />\n<br />\n以前，當我知道有這個能力後，曾盡力去告訴他們<br />\n<br />\n情況，更希望他們來得及親口與家人道別，但結果<br />\n<br />\n我相信大家都想到......"},{"pid":"49758c238314dbd94e47d4ca504442c0d241503d","tid":741488,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"重咁多時間作故嘅"},{"pid":"5d1940826d8aea31d605f1ce89f6ec1ed5316e24","tid":741488,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff54d3d5634de24d1298141ddf92a4c9567e649f","tid":741488,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"冇睇開故但個題材好似喺唔知邊到見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee83efbd81410c231024599b87dc1c1d7f838b6","tid":741488,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49758c238314dbd94e47d4ca504442c0d241503d","tid":741488,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"重咁多時間作故嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"夜晚見悶，個腦又塞塞地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849c338199f3ca5a4da9b5f46c1fa5213cc64ccc","tid":741488,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff54d3d5634de24d1298141ddf92a4c9567e649f","tid":741488,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"冇睇開故但個題材好似喺唔知邊到見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ef585884b30d4bce1fb0e09aae33d7d22eab5b","tid":741488,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"仙人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0555a13a355cd93ab8774bb508df461e7a0be46","tid":741488,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:10:06.000Z","msg":"「即時新聞」<br />\n<br />\n一名正返回公司的三十多歲男子，懷疑心急橫過馬<br />\n<br />\n路而被一輛貨車撞倒，當場死亡！司機因危險駕駛<br />\n<br />\n導致他人死亡被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閻王要你三更死，誰敢留人到五更<br />\n<br />\n以上的事情我已經見慣，習慣到毫無感覺，但只要<br />\n<br />\n我離開亞洲地區，能力就會失效......至少，我看不到<br />\n<br />\n身在英國的父母的死亡時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回到公司後又是一大堆工作，如果我有看到工作盡<br />\n<br />\n頭的能力而不是生命盡頭的能力就好了......<br />\n<br />\n「喂！阿邊個！做埋呢份入嚟，有份急嘅想你整咗先」<br />\n<br />\n他是我老闆吳清華，63歲，而他頭上倒數的時間...<br />\n<br />\n還有二十多年，算！忍你<br />\n<br />\n「係嘅！老細，俾多十分鐘我」<br />\n<br />\n「快快手！我會叫埋阿嗰個幫你」<br />\n<br />\n「即係邊個...呢！老細」<br />\n<br />\n「咪坐你後面戴眼鏡嗰個女仔囉！你唔好講住快快脆脆做埋佢啦！」<br />\n<br />\n她就是我其中一位同事，周芷晴，22歲，幸運的話<br />\n<br />\n我們可能已經是情侶，但有次在一家餐廳撞到她和<br />\n<br />\n她的父母，我看到她父母竟然是同時間死亡，後來<br />\n<br />\n我愚蠢到說了情況給她聽，當然...最後也是不相信<br />\n<br />\n我，結果......她的父母因一次旅行同時遇到交通意外<br />\n<br />\n死了，她一直認為是我詛咒她的父母"},{"pid":"567fbe3de97ad5fd8321a35d5776167752c76b24","tid":741488,"uid":27173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"好掛住仙人個校園故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d40d5e3e0ebe44aab75597db9895f7412315a60","tid":741488,"uid":164738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"你係咪叫夜神月呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f645774a30893324d2c44eb41480640fa9d99bfb","tid":741488,"uid":191156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d40d5e3e0ebe44aab75597db9895f7412315a60","tid":741488,"uid":164738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"你係咪叫夜神月呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T23:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仙人冇左一半壽命"},{"pid":"7803c6f4c1309390766eda756cb97423bddd5673","tid":741488,"uid":191156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d40d5e3e0ebe44aab75597db9895f7412315a60","tid":741488,"uid":164738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"你係咪叫夜神月呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T23:38:07.000Z","msg":"小心L出現 你做唔到新世界嘅神㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb0862a8ef1e63602e2fbb01f125874f97331f2","tid":741488,"uid":185696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T23:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仙人"},{"pid":"c8949f22604d55a6204efab0274c80eb90eeeec6","tid":741488,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:24:02.000Z","msg":"仙故留名"},{"pid":"ab96299c47b5f0b0d3254d3488577ab01bda0561","tid":741488,"uid":116143,"li